                            <comment id="13228133" author="thejas" created="Tue, 13 Mar 2012 01:57:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is possible to have multiple scalar variables in the limit expression, this will result in limit having multiple &apos;soft&apos; predecessors. This case also needs to be handled in the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
